<LanguageData>
  
  <!-- EN: Extra Heavy Multi-Legged Firepower Platform Main Cannon. -->
  <Wolfein_GiantTurret.label>火力平臺主炮</Wolfein_GiantTurret.label>
  <!-- EN: The main offensive system of the Extra Heavy Multi-Legged Firepower Platform; it can be said that the platform was designed primarily to deliver this heavy cannon to the frontline where it is needed most. -->
  <Wolfein_GiantTurret.description>超重型多足火力平臺的主要輸出手段，可以說火力平臺的設計目的就是將這門重型火炮送到前線需要它的地方。</Wolfein_GiantTurret.description>
  <!-- EN: Extra Heavy Multi-Legged Firepower Platform Main Cannon. -->
  <Wolfein_GiantTurret.verbs.Verb_Shoot.label>火力平臺主炮</Wolfein_GiantTurret.verbs.Verb_Shoot.label>
  
  <!-- EN: Extra Heavy Multi-Legged Firepower Platform Machine Gun. -->
  <Wolfein_GiantTurret_MechineGun.label>火力平臺機槍</Wolfein_GiantTurret_MechineGun.label>
  <!-- EN: A rapid-fire machine gun mounted on the turret, capable of clearing out units attempting to enter the main cannon』s blind spots.. -->
  <Wolfein_GiantTurret_MechineGun.description>安裝在炮塔上的速射機槍，足以清掃試圖進入主炮火力盲區的單位。</Wolfein_GiantTurret_MechineGun.description>
  <!-- EN: Extra Heavy Multi-Legged Firepower Platform Machine Gun. -->
  <Wolfein_GiantTurret_MechineGun.verbs.Verb_Shoot.label>超重型多足火力平臺機槍</Wolfein_GiantTurret_MechineGun.verbs.Verb_Shoot.label>
  
  <!-- EN: Basic Military Mech Unit -->
  <Wolfein_Mechanoid_MilitaryA.label>基礎型軍用機械體</Wolfein_Mechanoid_MilitaryA.label>
  <!-- EN: A product of reverse-engineering Mechanoid technology, this basic military mech is mass-produced by the MegaCorp and deployed to the frontlines to replace the steadily declining Wolfein soldier population. -->
  <Wolfein_Mechanoid_MilitaryA.description>基礎型軍用機械體，逆向分析機械族技術的產物，被軍企大批量部署到前線以代替日漸減少的沃芬族士兵。</Wolfein_Mechanoid_MilitaryA.description>
  <!-- EN: left fist -->
  <Wolfein_Mechanoid_MilitaryA.tools.left_fist.label>左拳</Wolfein_Mechanoid_MilitaryA.tools.left_fist.label>
  <!-- EN: right fist -->
  <Wolfein_Mechanoid_MilitaryA.tools.right_fist.label>右拳</Wolfein_Mechanoid_MilitaryA.tools.right_fist.label>
  
  <!-- EN: Close-Combat Military Mech Unit -->
  <Wolfein_Mechanoid_MilitaryB.label>近距型軍用機械體</Wolfein_Mechanoid_MilitaryB.label>
  <!-- EN: Designed for close-quarters engagement, this unit trades visual clarity for a wider field of view and heightened sensor sensitivity, allowing it to perform more effectively in short-range combat scenarios. -->
  <Wolfein_Mechanoid_MilitaryB.description>近距型軍用機械體，以犧牲視覺感測器清晰度為代價換來了大視場和高靈敏度，使其在近距作戰中表現更佳。</Wolfein_Mechanoid_MilitaryB.description>
  <!-- EN: left fist -->
  <Wolfein_Mechanoid_MilitaryB.tools.left_fist.label>左拳</Wolfein_Mechanoid_MilitaryB.tools.left_fist.label>
  <!-- EN: right fist -->
  <Wolfein_Mechanoid_MilitaryB.tools.right_fist.label>右拳</Wolfein_Mechanoid_MilitaryB.tools.right_fist.label>
  
  <!-- EN: Shielded Military Mech Unit -->
  <Wolfein_Mechanoid_MilitaryC.label>盾衛型軍用機械體</Wolfein_Mechanoid_MilitaryC.label>
  <!-- EN: Equipped with a heavy shield and an impact drill, this unit excels at close-range encounters with heavily armored mech targets. Its drill's exceptional destructive power against structures also makes it a frequent choice for demolition operations. -->
  <Wolfein_Mechanoid_MilitaryC.description>盾衛型軍用機械體，配備的盾牌和衝擊鉆讓其在貼身處理重灌甲機械族時效率出衆。由於其衝擊鉆對建築物的破壞力驚人，也被經常部署于破拆建築。</Wolfein_Mechanoid_MilitaryC.description>
  <!-- EN: left fist -->
  <Wolfein_Mechanoid_MilitaryC.tools.left_fist.label>左拳</Wolfein_Mechanoid_MilitaryC.tools.left_fist.label>
  <!-- EN: right fist -->
  <Wolfein_Mechanoid_MilitaryC.tools.right_fist.label>右拳</Wolfein_Mechanoid_MilitaryC.tools.right_fist.label>
  <!-- EN: Heavy shield -->
  <Wolfein_Mechanoid_MilitaryC.tools.Heavy_shield.label>盾牌</Wolfein_Mechanoid_MilitaryC.tools.Heavy_shield.label>
  <!-- EN: Impact drill -->
  <Wolfein_Mechanoid_MilitaryC.tools.Impact_drill.label>衝擊鉆</Wolfein_Mechanoid_MilitaryC.tools.Impact_drill.label>
  
  <!-- EN: Sniper-Class Military Mech Unit -->
  <Wolfein_Mechanoid_MilitaryD.label>狙擊型軍用機械體</Wolfein_Mechanoid_MilitaryD.label>
  <!-- EN: In addition to upgraded sensors, this unit features heat-insulating skirt armor on its torso, reducing the chance of infrared detection compared to the standard model. -->
  <Wolfein_Mechanoid_MilitaryD.description>狙擊型軍用機械體，除去感測器的升級外，相比基礎型號在軀幹部位加裝了隔熱裙甲，降低被紅外線探測到的概率。</Wolfein_Mechanoid_MilitaryD.description>
  <!-- EN: left fist -->
  <Wolfein_Mechanoid_MilitaryD.tools.left_fist.label>左拳</Wolfein_Mechanoid_MilitaryD.tools.left_fist.label>
  <!-- EN: right fist -->
  <Wolfein_Mechanoid_MilitaryD.tools.right_fist.label>右拳</Wolfein_Mechanoid_MilitaryD.tools.right_fist.label>
  
  <!-- EN: Heavy Fire Support Mech Unit -->
  <Wolfein_Mechanoid_MilitaryE.label>重型火力支援步行機械體</Wolfein_Mechanoid_MilitaryE.label>
  <!-- EN: The heavy fire support Mech Unit serves primarily as an all-terrain platform for mounting heavy weaponry. According to reports, members of the MegaCorp Task Force experience an average 50% morale boost when advancing alongside one. -->
  <Wolfein_Mechanoid_MilitaryE.description>重型火力支援步行機械體，主要作為全地形的重型武器搭載平臺來使用。據統計，軍企機動特遣隊的成員們在伴隨步行機進攻時士氣平均提升50%。</Wolfein_Mechanoid_MilitaryE.description>
  <!-- EN: left fist -->
  <Wolfein_Mechanoid_MilitaryE.tools.left_fist.label>左拳</Wolfein_Mechanoid_MilitaryE.tools.left_fist.label>
  <!-- EN: right fist -->
  <Wolfein_Mechanoid_MilitaryE.tools.right_fist.label>右拳</Wolfein_Mechanoid_MilitaryE.tools.right_fist.label>
  
  <!-- EN: Heavy Close-Range Support Mech Unit. -->
  <Wolfein_Mechanoid_MilitaryF.label>重型近程支援步行機械體</Wolfein_Mechanoid_MilitaryF.label>
  <!-- EN: The Heavy Close-Range Support Mech Unit, unlike units tasked with mid-to-long-range fire support, is equipped with additional armor and a large shield, making it better suited for providing mid-to-close-range support to other mechanical units. -->
  <Wolfein_Mechanoid_MilitaryF.description>重型近程支援步行機械體，與其承擔中遠端火力支援任務的機體不同，附加的額外裝甲和大型護盾使其更適合承擔中近距離支援其他機械體的任務。</Wolfein_Mechanoid_MilitaryF.description>
  <!-- EN: left fist -->
  <Wolfein_Mechanoid_MilitaryF.tools.left_fist.label>左拳</Wolfein_Mechanoid_MilitaryF.tools.left_fist.label>
  <!-- EN: right fist -->
  <Wolfein_Mechanoid_MilitaryF.tools.right_fist.label>右拳</Wolfein_Mechanoid_MilitaryF.tools.right_fist.label>
  
  <!-- EN: Extra Heavy Multi-Legged Firepower Platform. -->
  <Wolfein_Mechanoid_MilitaryGiant.label>超重型多足火力平臺</Wolfein_Mechanoid_MilitaryGiant.label>
  <!-- EN: The extra heavy multi-legged firepower platform, the largest active mech in the MegaCorp arsenal, requires approval from the highest local military authority for each deployment. Its weapons are powerful enough to breach the enemy's most fortified defenses after just a few shots. -->
  <Wolfein_Mechanoid_MilitaryGiant.description>超重型多足火力平臺，作為軍企現役最大的機械體，其每次部署都需要當地最高軍事主管的批準。而其上配置的武器足以在數次開火后撕開敵方最嚴密的防線。</Wolfein_Mechanoid_MilitaryGiant.description>
  <!-- EN: blunt -->
  <Wolfein_Mechanoid_MilitaryGiant.tools.blunt.label>鈍擊</Wolfein_Mechanoid_MilitaryGiant.tools.blunt.label>
